description:
qualifier that specifies a product lifecycle stage or phase in which the assigned value is applicable.
1 The value list is used in the energy transmission and distribution sector for the period of operation of an item., 2 A qualifier with a different value list of another technical domain may be registered with the same name but with a different identifier , 3 The current value list may be expanded in future versions of the reference dictionary. , 4 The current value list may be expanded on the fly when there is an agreement among the exchange partners.
